                        revealing patterns, and helping you cut costs—all in an intuitive, data-rich interface.
                    </p>

                    <div class="row my-5">
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                            <div class="feature">
                                <div class="icon p-2">
                                    <span class="fa fa-sliders fa-2x text-black">
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Fast & Simple Setup</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Start monitoring your energy usage within minutes. Connect, tag devices, and get real insights without needing technical knowledge.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                            <div class="feature">
                                <div class="icon p-2">
                                    <span class="fa fa-chart-line fa-2x text-black">
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Visual Energy Insights</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Interactive graphs and personalized dashboards let you explore real-time and historical consumption—making energy-saving decisions effortless.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                            <div class="feature">
                                <div class="icon p-2">
                                    <span class="fa fa-laptop-code fa-2x text-black">
                                    </span>
                                </div>
